1) Program for swapping of two numbers without using third variable
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
a=int(input('enter a value'))
b=int(input('enter b value'))
a=a+b
b=a-b
a=a-b
print('a value is:',a ,'b value is:',b)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
enter a value 10
enter b value 20
a value is: 20 b value is: 10
******************************************************************************
